{"tid":2368468,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"父力證清白 青年庭上哭泣","createTime":"2021-01-16T08:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T08:33:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c04a06243b6154f2a9b4254e29f1aed0ee17582","tid":2368468,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:23:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/SH2NGEBQZ5AT3LGRYM6BQUGUYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FSH2NGEBQZ5AT3LGRYM6BQUGUYM%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyE5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=74d7db00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FSH2NGEBQZ5AT3LGRYM6BQUGUYM%2F&h=fd703b4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/SH2NGEBQZ5AT3LGRYM6BQUGUYM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n父力證清白 青年庭上哭泣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JMgz7kL7htMK64cPAvYRM_KPAUA=/624x351/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TJA5WZAXC5CD3CQK56T7F7QJZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJMgz7kL7htMK64cPAvYRM_KPAUA%3D%2F624x351%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTJA5WZAXC5CD3CQK56T7F7QJZI.jpg&h=95088486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■兩被告林志威（圖）及黃博昕昨被裁定表證成立。<br />\n<br />\n【藏噴漆案】【本報訊】民陣前年12月1日發起「毋忘初心大遊行」，事前獲發不反對通知書，但警方途中在尖沙嘴一帶舉起藍旗並且驅散群眾，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Za3M2VQoPYvCDJeuSWpvdAIPXrU=/818x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SSCCPCGUDFEGHHAFHLQ4TYR3GE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZa3M2VQoPYvCDJeuSWpvdAIPXrU%3D%2F818x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSSCCPCGUDFEGHHAFHLQ4TYR3GE.jpg&h=5b318af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃博昕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lEKP-IjhtG0pI8ZdzuWlgF0lK_A=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3PDELHJ54VF5DJGUUB2OFQJFHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlEKP-IjhtG0pI8ZdzuWlgF0lK_A%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3PDELHJ54VF5DJGUUB2OFQJFHU.jpg&h=c45b1712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■案中毋忘初心大遊行獲警方不反對通知書，但其後被警腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方：市民斥警阻合法遊行<br />\n<br />\n兩被告。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「速龍」小隊成員佘裕城供稱，他與同袍進入梳士巴利道公園，被百多人包圍及指罵「死黑警」，同袍用揚聲器宣稱那是非法集會，要求示威者離開，惟黃僅周圍望。他懷疑黃參與非法集結，衝前將黃按在地上。<br />\n<br />\n佘事發翌日凌晨錄取首份證人供詞，但沒提及黃被捕前的細節，至半年後第二份證人供詞才提及，遭辯方質疑。佘解釋黃是他在反修例運動中首名截停、亦是最後一名截停的被告，故印象深刻。辯方又指當時有市民質疑警方謂：「呢個係合法遊行！點解趕我走？」佘稱聽不到。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉啟亮裁定兩被告表證成立，任裝修工的林自辯稱案發當日參與合法遊行，聽到有市民大喊：「舉咗藍旗啦！快啲走！」未幾他便被警員制服。<br />\n<br />\n控方指林。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n擔任辯方證人的林父供稱，前年8月兒子開始在其公司任油漆工，他曾交帶兒子案發當日到華潤大廈取黑色噴漆，以便翌日於科學園補漆時用。父親作供時，林一度哭泣。案件下周五續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC1275/20"},{"pid":"e98e674b78f6c71dddfd38a77be2091642693ea8","tid":2368468,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"上訴呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31873b8a26e078ff97544e7402dd96883a7567cd","tid":2368468,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e98e674b78f6c71dddfd38a77be2091642693ea8","tid":2368468,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"上訴呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"